ues, providing innovative treatment, and offering patients new levels</span><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt"> of medical care.  Some one million patients are treated at HMO each year.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 14pt; padding-left:4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">HMO is a national referral center for the most complex and challenging medical cases, in addition to serving the one million residents of the greater Jerusalem area. We also treat </span><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">patients from Palestine, neighboring regions and other countries around the world. Housing the only Level IA trauma center in the greater Jerusalem area, HMO has created many centers of excellence and has developed unique facilities, many of which are the </span><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">only services of their kind in the entire country or in the greater Jerusalem area. A premier teaching hospital and research center performing more than half the hospital based research in the country, HMO is equipped with the most sophisticated diagnostic</span><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">, treatment and research equipment. Hadassah is dedicated to helping and healing, to changing - and saving - people's lives.  </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="4" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 14pt; padding-left:4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Sylfaen; font-size:12pt">Since inception, despite many challenges, HMO has success